\f1\b Revised Detailed Summary with Constraints for LLM Rewrite:
\f0\b0 \

\f1\b Logline:
\f0\b0  Two individuals from vastly different realities\'97one a resident of a seemingly perfect but subtly glitching world, the other a resourceful survivor in a harsh, technology-scarce environment\'97uncover a shocking truth connecting their existences and must bridge their worlds to prevent a catastrophic system collapse. 
\f2\i \strokec2 (Constraint for LLM: The nature of the connection and the "system" should remain mysterious until the designated reveal point.)
\f0\i0 \strokec2 \

\f1\b Overall Structure:
\f0\b0  The story MUST begin by introducing Leo and Anya in their entirely separate realities, focusing on the contrasts and unexplained mysteries of their worlds. Their paths converge only after a significant midpoint revelation. The plot follows: Separate Introductions -> One-Way Observation -> Partial Information -> The Big Reveal -> Direct Connection -> Collaboration -> Climax -> Resolution. 
\f2\i \strokec2 (Constraint for LLM: Strictly adhere to this sequential structure. Do NOT introduce interaction or mutual awareness between Leo and Anya before the specified points.)
