\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Anya's World (Reality B - The Real World):
\f0\b0  Introduce Anya living in a starkly contrasting world \'96 a community surviving through manual labor, close connection to nature, and scavenging resources from dangerous, decaying "dead cities" filled with remnants of advanced technology. Technology ("robot stuff") is feared and misunderstood by her community. Anya is an outsider due to her fascination with salvaging and repairing old tech based on forbidden books, driven by curiosity but isolated. The reason for the "dead cities" and the fear of tech is rooted in forgotten history, presented as a mystery.\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Constraint for LLM (Phase 1): In these opening scenes, Leo and Anya MUST exist in entirely separate realities with NO knowledge or awareness of each other. Focus ONLY on establishing their individual circumstances, the unique characteristics and mysteries of their respective worlds (Leo's glitches/artificiality, Anya's harsh survival/tech taboo), and their personal feelings (Leo's detachment, Anya's isolation/curiosity). Do NOT hint at the Simulation yet.\
